> ask Percy about camera

> ask Percy about camera
"Ah yes, this is a new-fangled sort of painting, I hear.  Uses mercury fumes or something to capture images as they appear in reality. Of course, if you have a daguerreotype image, it's a great way to prove that something actually happened... since they can't be faked! I mean, how are you going to make a fake reality?"
