Not right now, you feel like your face isn't complete for a photo yet.
> wear eyepatch

> wear eyepatch
You pull the band around your head and snap the patch over your left eye.  The left eye is as good an eye as any to cover, after all.
> use tintamarresque

> use tintamarresque
You stick your head through the hole.  "Oi! C'mon, take a picture of me now!"

The carnie dutifully sets up her daguerreotype camera and holds up a tray of chlorate powder.  "Smile!"

After a blinding flash and loud BANG, you're left alone in the room as the carnie retires into the back to develop the photo.  After a good long wait, she emerges and hands you a daguerreotype photo.

"Congratulations on your beach vacation," she says flatly.
