You are on the factory floor.
The factory floor is a wide-open, cavernous room. Your footsteps echo loudly against the metal floor as you walk. There are puddles of water here and there, formed from the steady drip drip drip of absorbed rainwater trickling down from above.  There are also big snowdrift-sized lumps of congealed rubber throughout the room.

You turn suddenly and catch sight of something small and spindly leaning over to drink from one of the puddles. The creature straightens up and swivels to face you as it realizes that it's been exposed in the glare of your lamp.  It's a small articulated doll with a porcelain head and a crinoline dress. It pauses for just a second and then scampers off into the dark.
