As you scale the ladder, you notice Red and Mugsy emerging from the office, both still covered in ichor and both wild-eyed with confusion.

"Crumbs!" shouts Red as he catches sight of you. "A clown!"

"I ain't no clown," you snap. "It's me, Lil' Ragamuffin! I is wearin' a disguise!"

"Wot's goin' on here?" demands Red, "Hey, toots, wot gives?"

"I ain't got time fer you two mugs," you say, "But you's better get outta here, a'fore this place blows ta Kingdom Come! Get!"

"Criminey! C'mon, Red, let's leg it!" squeals Mugsy.

The two of them go pinwheeling off into the darkness of the catwalk, their running footsteps echoing in the thick, sweltering air.
