The walls of the entryway are painted a deep crimson red, giving you the distinct impression that you're traveling down some monstrous creature's throat.
You can see a crimson clown.
You can go south or north.
There he is-- that crimson clown that was blocking your escape this whole time!  His face is still frozen in the same rictis grin and he hulks his shoulders, ready for a fight.

You're ready for him.

"Now who's laughing!?" you shout as you gun your bumper car right into him, throwing him to the ground in a crimson blur. "Me, that's who!"
